T1  - The incremental information content of bond rating revisions: The Australian evidence
AU  - Matolcsy, Z.P.
AU  - Lianto, T.
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 19
IS  - 5
SP  - 891
EP  - 902
PY  - 1995
